                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 200.549,
                                "stop": 207.547,
                                "byte_start": 830945,
                                "byte_stop": 858948,
                                "text": "Then the legislative entirely is in (Inaudible)"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 207.547,
                        "stop": 246.623,
                        "byte_start": 858948,
                        "byte_stop": 1015265,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 16091,
                            "name": "Mr. Attorney General",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/attorney_general",
                            "last_name": "General",
                            "roles": null,
                            "thumbnail": null,
                            "length_of_service": 0,
                            "identifier": "attorney_general"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 207.547,
                                "stop": 213.453,
                                "byte_start": 858948,
                                "byte_stop": 882563,
                                "text": "Apparently not."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 213.453,
                                "stop": 222.93,
                                "byte_start": 882563,
                                "byte_stop": 920492,
                                "text": "Now, I concede to the fact that advocates in this area are not in the same class as redheads as I suggested."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 222.93,
                                "stop": 231.577,
                                "byte_start": 920492,
                                "byte_stop": 955079,
                                "text": "But in determining the validity of this and the purpose, we have to look at two purposes."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 231.577,
                                "stop": 237.811,
                                "byte_start": 955079,
                                "byte_stop": 979947,
                                "text": "One, the purpose of the exemption, it\u0027s the Article 20, the constitutional amendment itself."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 237.811,
                                "stop": 245.763,
                                "byte_start": 979947,
                                "byte_stop": 1011816,
                                "text": "And then secondly, we have to consider the purposes of all exemptions and see whether there is a broad overall purpose."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 245.763,
                                "stop": 246.623,
                                "byte_start": 1011816,
                                "byte_stop": 1015265,
                                "text": "Now, the --"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 246.623,
                        "stop": 252.013,
                        "byte_start": 1015265,
                        "byte_stop": 1036790,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15140,
                            "name": "William J. Brennan, Jr.",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/william_j_brennan_jr",
                            "last_name": "Brennan",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2786,
